@startuml Saga-Orchestrator-State
!theme plain
skinparam state {
BackgroundColor<<success>> LightGreen
BackgroundColor<<error>> LightCoral
BorderColor Black
}

[*] --> OrderPlaced : PlaceOrderCommand
OrderPlaced --> PaymentInitiated : Enviar InitiatePayment
PaymentInitiated --> PaymentAuthorized : Esperar PaymentAuthorized
PaymentAuthorized --> RestaurantNotified : Enviar CreateRestaurantOrder
RestaurantNotified --> RestaurantAccepted : Esperar RestaurantOrderAccepted
RestaurantAccepted --> DeliveryCreated : Enviar CreateDelivery
DeliveryCreated --> DeliveryDelivered : Esperar DeliveryDelivered
DeliveryDelivered --> OrderDelivered : OrderDelivered
OrderDelivered --> [*] : SagaSuccess <<success>>

PaymentInitiated --> PaymentFailed : PaymentFailed
PaymentFailed --> OrderCancelled : CancelOrder
OrderCancelled --> [*] : SagaAborted <<error>>

RestaurantNotified --> RestaurantRejected : RestaurantOrderRejected
RestaurantRejected --> RefundPayment : RefundPayment
RefundPayment --> OrderCancelled : OrderCancelled
OrderCancelled --> [*] : SagaAborted <<error>>

DeliveryCreated --> DeliveryFailed : DeliveryStatusChanged(FAILED)
DeliveryFailed --> PartialRefund : RefundPayment(partial)
PartialRefund --> OrderFailed : OrderFailed
OrderFailed --> [*] : SagaFailed <<error>>

note right of SagaAborted
Compensações executadas:

- Refund Payment
- Cancel Delivery (se existir)
  end note

@enduml
